INCLINATION.desc: Reaction Wheel axis above the XY Plane, this should be in a RW config, equal to np.pi / 3

AZIMUTH.desc: reaction wheel axis from the x-y axes

LENGTH.desc: Length of the satellite, wall to wall (please define axis)

WIDTH.desc: Width of the satellite, wall to wall (please define axis)

HEIGHT.desc: Height of the satellite, wall to wall (please define axis)

PRINCIPAL.desc: Principal moment of inertia for without reaction wheels
